name: Alpha Series Ziggurats 4023
description: Legend tells of ancient death cults and amazing jewelry.  Conspiracy theorists have often linked the world's Ziggurats to aliens and other worlds.  Who knew they might actually be on to something. This guy arrived in the colony bathed in blood and babbling in a language that no one understands.  He is having a grand old time at the colony so far, and loves the forests around the city.
